<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Support Shalo</title>

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    background:#f5f7fb;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    width:350px;
    padding:35px;
    border-radius:20px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.logo{
    font-size:60px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

h1{
    color:#222;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

p{
    color:#555;
    line-height:1.7;
}

.donate-btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:25px;
    padding:15px 30px;
    background:#0070ba;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:12px;
    font-size:18px;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.donate-btn:hover{
    background:#005ea6;
}

.share{
    margin-top:20px;
    color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

    <div class="logo">❤️</div>

    <h1>Support Shalo</h1>

    <p>
        Hey,<br><br>
        I'm hoping you'll consider supporting the good work Shalo does
        by donating or sharing with others who'd like to help.
    </p>

    <a class="donate-btn"
       href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=B69Z3EL5YPG7W"
       target="_blank">
       Donate with PayPal
    </a>

    <div class="share">
        Thank you for your kindness and support 🙏
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>